            <p class="message">
                We're thrilled to have you join our community! Your account has been successfully created 
                and you're all set to explore everything we have to offer.
            </p>
            
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <h3>ðŸ“§ Your Account Details</h3>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
                <p><strong>Registration Date:</strong> <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }) %></p>
            </div>
            
            <p class="message">
                To get started, simply log in with your credentials and explore all the features 
                available to you. If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team 
                is always here to help.
            </p>
            
            <center>
                <a href="<%= loginUrl || 'http://localhost:5000/api/users/login' %>" class="cta-button">
                    Get Started Now
                </a>
            </center>
            
            <div class="highlight-box">
