                    â€¢ Enable two-factor authentication for extra security<br>
                    â€¢ Contact us immediately if you notice any suspicious activity
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing our platform!</p>
            <p>If you didn't create this account, please contact us immediately.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; color: #aaa; font-size: 12px;">
                Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> TechyJaunt Academy. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
